short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: Export your STARS timetable to your favorite calendar app!

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: STARSCal is a Chrome extension that allows NTU students to easily customise and export their timetables from the NTU STARS system to their favourite calendar application.
